<strong>WORKS CITED</strong>
<br><br>
Add a &#8216;Works Cited&#8217; entry at the end of your essay citing all sources used in the body of your writing.
<br><br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br><br>
When an entry starts with a government agency, begin the entry with the name of the government followed by a comma then the name of the agency. 
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	Name of Government, Name of Department or Agency. <em>Title</em>. Year of publication, URL. 
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	<span class="hover" title="Name of Government">Australian Government</span>,
	<span class="hover" title="Name of Department or Agency">Department of Health and Ageing</span>.
	<em><span class="hover" title="Title">Ageing and Aged Care in Australia</span></em>.
	<span class="hover" title="Year of publication">2008</span>,
	<span class="hover" title="URL">www.health.gov.au/internet/main/publishing.nsf/Content/ageing</span>.
</blockquote>
